\section{U.S. Inflation, Unemployment, and Business Cycles}
\begin{enumerate}
  \item Describe in lots of detail Demand-Pull inflation.
  \item Describe in lots of detail Cost-Push inflation.
  \item Describe the effect of expected inflation.
  \item Describe the short-run Phillips curve.
  \item Describe the long-run Phillips curve.
  \item Provide a brief overview of the following mainstream business cycle theories:
  \begin{enumerate}
    \item Keynesian Cycle Theory.
    \item Monetarist Cycle Theory.
    \item New Classical Cycle Theory.
    \item New Keynesian Cycle Theory.
  \end{enumerate}
  \item Describe in great detail the real business cycle theory.
  \item What are the criticisms and defenses of RBC theory?
\end{enumerate}

